es.upv.grc.grcbox.server.multicastProxy

Class MulticastProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.upv.grc.grcbox.server.multicastProxy.MulticastProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ScampiProxy

    public class MulticastProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    A simple multicast proxy that forwards multicast packets between both interfaces. If a protocol requires to modified any field of the packet payload, this class must be specialised by implementing the method processPayloadIncoming(byte[] payload) and processPayloadOutgoing(byte[] payload).
